Minimalism
==========

A simple Sphinx_ theme inspired by `Flasks documentation`_.

In order for this theme to work `theme_style.py` has to be in the
`PYTHONPATH` or `sys.path`.

Options:

`github_fork`
   The name of the Github project in the form `username/project`, if set
   this will display a Forkme ribbon.

.. _Sphinx: http://sphinx.pocoo.org/
.. _Flasks documentation: http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/
